ygData.subject: Re: Hell Level question
ygData.msgSnippet: This may sound unbelievable but I went thru 30 in 1 day in Highkeep.  I played around 18hrs that day but I was always in a good group and I only died only once
ygData.messageBody:
This may sound unbelievable but I went thru 30 in 1 day in Highkeep. I
played around 18hrs that day but I was always in a good group and I only
died only once and that was because there were only 10 people in the zone
and trains were horrible. I stayed in Highkeep til I reached 34 then
ventured to Solb. Now I am currently in Hell level 35.

Zarina D`Haven
Rallos Zek
